Package org.gridlab.gat.util Description

This package contains classes and interfaces which are of general use for the GAT application API. The most important classes and interfaces in this package are Collection, TimePeriod, and Buffer. An instance of the class Collection represents a collection, a group of objects which are known as elements, and is used to manipulate such. An instance of the class TimePeriod represents a time period. An instance of the class Buffer is a container for data.
